<item>
            <title>[LU-10734] sanity test_160g: User cl8 still found in changelog_users</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10734</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;sanity test_160g - User cl8 still found in changelog_users&lt;br/&gt;
^^^^^^^^^^^^^ DO NOT REMOVE LINE ABOVE ^^^^^^^^^^^^^&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Bob Glossman &amp;lt;bob.glossman@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/5a8495f4-1bfa-11e8-a6ad-52540065bddc&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/5a8495f4-1bfa-11e8-a6ad-52540065bddc&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/34e243bc-1be3-11e8-a7cd-52540065bddc&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/34e243bc-1be3-11e8-a7cd-52540065bddc&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;test_160g failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;User cl8 still found in changelog_users
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This may be a dup of &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-9624&quot; title=&quot;enable sanity.sh test_160a failures for DNE&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-9624&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-9624&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
I can&apos;t tell if it is so I am raising a fresh ticket.&lt;br/&gt;
Will let somebody else decide if it&apos;s a dup or not.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
