                            <comment id="230424" author="gerrit" created="Wed, 18 Jul 2018 05:59:26 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Oleg Drokin (green@whamcloud.com) merged in patch &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/31604/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/31604/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
Subject: &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10734&quot; title=&quot;sanity test_160g: User cl8 still found in changelog_users&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-10734&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-10734&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; tests: ensure current GC interval is over&lt;br/&gt;
