                            <comment id="222162" author="bfaccini" created="Fri, 2 Mar 2018 21:27:35 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Well, it is strange that it seems to only fail running with SLES, and looks like it started to fail after my 1st patch for &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10680&quot; title=&quot;MDT becoming unresponsive in 2.10.3&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-10680&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-10680&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (&lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/31347/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/31347/&lt;/a&gt;) has landed, when it should fix an issue with my previous patch for &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7340&quot; title=&quot;ChangeLogs catalog full condition should be handled more gracefully&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-7340&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-7340&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; which has introduced sanity/test_160&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;f,g&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; tests !!... I think I need to reproduce and debug it this way.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
